   <title xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Creating a collection from search results</title>
   <procedure xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
      <title>To create a collection from search results:</title>
      <para>In the search panel, search for and filter the items you want to add to a collection.</para>
      <para>Mark the checkboxes for the items you want to add to the collection.</para>
      <para>Under Actions, click New Collection.</para>
      <para>The Save Collection widget appears.</para>
      <para>In the Save Collection widget type a name for the collection.</para>
      <para>Click Save.</para>
   </procedure>
